subject: Re: [junit] Re: A JUnit extension for regression test prioritization
msgSnippet: ... The JUnit tests are part of the JUnit package, but they are not in junit.jar. When you expand the .zip, you should see the source for the tests. -- J. B.
messageBody:
mjrummel2000 wrote:

> My apologies, I was able to find the test cases for JUnit and cruise

The JUnit tests are part of the JUnit package, but they are not in
junit.jar. When you expand the .zip, you should see the source for the
tests.
